Zip to text:
============
[System.Convert]::ToBase64String([System.IO.File]::ReadAllBytes("path\to\file.zip")) | Set-Content "path\to\file.txt"
 
 
Text to Zip:
============
[System.IO.File]::WriteAllBytes("path\to\file.zip",[System.Convert]::FromBase64String([System.IO.File]::ReadAllText("path\to\file.txt")))
